
To compile a file ——> javac file_name.java
To interprete a file ——> java file_name.class or only java file_name
To move all files to their corresponding packages ——> javac -d . *.java
To move a file to its corresponding package ——> javac -d . file_name.java
To move all files to their corresponding packages in a folder by creating that folder ——> javac -d folder_name *.java
To move a file to its corresponding package in a folder by creating that folder ——> javac -d folder_name file_name.java
